  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[On Play][When Digivolving] If there're 6 or fewer total
    cards in both players' security stacks, gain 3 memory, and reveal 1 card in your
    hand. If it\u2019s yellow, place it on top of your security stack face down.
    If it's not, return it to the hand.[When Attacking][Once Per Turn] By trashing
    the top card of your security stack, unsuspend this Digimon, and 1 of your opponent's
    Digimon gets -7000 DP for the turn."
